Automata.name: Single Visual Project
Automata.comment: The 'Atelier Inter-établissement de Productique' (AIP) example described in 'Hierarchical Interface-based Supervisory Control' by R.J. Leduc. Here, the silly 'NewEvents'-models have been removed, otherwise everything is as in the report except for the names of the models which vary slightly. The models can be divided into three disjoint groups - TU4, AS3 and the rest - having no events in common. The model being incomplete has to do with the limitation of the methods used in the mentioned thesis.
